Package safenet.jcprov.params Description

Provides parameter structure/class definitions used by some mechanisms.

With regards to parameters, there are three types of mechanism :-

  • Those that take no parameter

  • Those that take a simple parameter (e.g. long, byte[])

  • Those that take a complex parameter - a structure

    • This package contains the classes which define the complex parameters. The data fields in the classes are public because they represent a collection of data, i.e. structures, as opposed to data and methods, i.e. classes.
